-1 Kyorlites~
.

The Kyorlites have recently emerged from hiding to let their purpose be
known.  For thousands of years they have remained in secrecy, plotting their
return to power as they claim is rightfully theirs.  They have but one goal,
to prepare the world for the coming of their supreme master, Kyorl.  Only
thought to be a monster from children's stories, this deity is painfully
real.  Known to his faithful as the Lord of Shadows, he was imprisoned
thousands of years ago by the combined effort of both the forces of Darkness
and Light.  Since his disappearance from this plane of existence, people
eventually forgot about his terrible power and of Kyorl altogether.  But the
Master of the Demon World bidded his time, knowing that some day he would
find a way to escape from his prison and unleash his vengeance upon the
mortal realm.  Eventually Kyorl found the answer to his dilemma, a young
Titan by the name of Mordread that was born with an immense hidden power. 
The Lord of the Shadows spoke with the Sorcerer, and showed him the path to
unlocking his massive strength.  In return all Kyorl asked was that Mordread
help him exact his revenge.  From that day on, Mordread spent every waking
moment of his life furthering the wishes of his Dark Master.  He formed the
organization that became known as the Kyorlites, and quickly their ranks
amassed.  Closely approaching their goal, Kyorl has ordered his followers to
rise from the shadows once again.  Spreading fear across the land, the
Kyorlites align themselves with no one.  The choices of those that inhabit
this world are very clear.  Join the Kyorlites in their unrelenting quest,
order all rescue baodwyn be swallowed by the Shadows never to be heard from
again.  
~

