-1 STARTCLAN~
Joining a clan or starting a new one can be both rewarding and hard work. Here
on Death Rising (DR) a few rules go with both starting and being in a clan.
Below are the rules for starting a new clan.

1)  There must be two level 50 tier 2 people involved in creating and obtaining
the clan.

2)  A new clan will cost you 100 IQP plus 500 IQP for a clan hall for a total of 600.

3)  Clan rooms, mobs, and objects will be described by *YOU* but built by Loki.

                           ***Role-play Rules***
1)  Clan must be role-play oriented. (Clan name included)

2)  You must have a history of your clan written, it can be posted as a note to
Loki or emailed to death_rising_implementor@hotmail.com. This history must 
include how your clan became into exsistance, what it stands for, and what you
intend to accomplish with this clan. Also it must be well written.

3)  You and your members are expected to RP in any public channels or rooms. This
excludes the (OOC) channel. Here on DR the RP definition is very loose, but direct
insults included inappropriate language will **NOT** be tolerated. Also talking about
things from RL is not RP, thats why the (OOC) channel is there. 

